title: Heritage nomination might save Batemans Bay's early settler buildings
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Heritage nomination might save Batema... Heritage nomination might save Batemans Bay's early settler buildings Next Story Prev Story 3 hrs ago Read more: ABC News 
It seems a fortuitous accident that two of Batemans Bay's original buildings still exist but some fear they may soon be demolished. They've survived decades of development around them but now they are in the sights of developers aiming to build a car park. Start the conversation, or Read more at ABC News.
